246
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,721
<i>I get lost in the language.</i>
<i>Words like:</i>

247
00:16:42,896 --> 00:16:44,056
<i>"Thither."</i>

248
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:46,095
<i>"Mischance."</i>

249
00:16:46,266 --> 00:16:47,961
<i>"Felicity."</i>

250
00:16:48,668 --> 00:16:51,296
<i>I'm always in agony over whether</i>
