251
00:16:51,471 --> 00:16:53,803
<i>... are really going to get together.</i>

252
00:16:54,074 --> 00:16:55,234
<i>Read it.</i>

253
00:16:55,475 --> 00:16:57,568
<i>I know you'll love it.</i>

254
00:16:59,012 --> 00:17:00,843
JOE: <i>The purpose of places</i>
<i>like Starbucks...</i>

255
00:17:01,014 --> 00:17:03,482
<i>... is for people with</i>
<i>no decision-making ability...</i>

256
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:07,379
